BART Data Analytics: Passenger Concentration vs. Time of Day/Station

The below data table is the raw data set used to form the foundation of our BART commmute patterns analysis.

The data was manipulated through Python and transposed into a MongoDB database. The visualizations were created through a variety of tools, including D3 and Leaflet.

The dataset was taken from Kaggle.
